frus:attachment.head:
The American Minister in Saudi Arabia (
    Eddy
) to the Saudi Arabian Acting Minister for
    Foreign Affairs (
    Yassin
)

frus:attachment.p:
The air route for which the above installations are required will extend from
                        Cairo, Egypt, to Dhahran, Saudi Arabia, by way of Ma’an, Trans-Jordan;
                        Lauqa, Saudi Arabia; and Hafar al Batin, Saudi Arabia.

frus:attachment.head:
The American Minister in Saudi Arabia (
    Eddy
) to the Saudi Arabian Acting Minister for
    Foreign Affairs (
    Yassin
)
